title: North Esports Preseason Highlights!!

embed.description: This video is a highlight reel of the North Esports League of Legends team and their journey throughout the Oceania 5v5 Preseason Tournament. Hope you guys enjoy! Help support our LOL team as they embark on their journey to make it through to the OPL!

body:
North Esports is one of the newest teams in the OCE scene trying to push for the OPL. Watch them in this Preseason tournament dominate all teams and take out the title!
